title.rendered: St Jago wins 2024 Schools’ Challenge Quiz | News

content.rendered:
St Jago High School has proven itself again to be the all-island champion in the TVJ’s 2024 Schools’ Challenge Quiz competition for the third consecutive year against Calabar High School. 

After a sudden death round, St Jago defeated Calabar 37-33. 

Tonight’s victory is the eighth for the Monk Street, St Catherine institution.

This is also the 13th final match for St Jago. 

– Ainsworth Morris
